&lt;li&gt;Proactively source, identify, research, and engage active and passive candidates via LinkedIn, GitHub, Djinni, job boards, referrals, and niche communities (quant, code/dev, competitive programming), leveraging creative sourcing strategies (Boolean search, social networks, community channels).&lt;/li&gt;
