&lt;li&gt;Partner with senior recruiters and hiring managers to support the full recruitment cycle, including interview coordination, scheduling, and calendar management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and update the ATS, ensure accurate daily candidate status tracking, and support overall pipeline hygiene.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support market and talent research (hiring trends, layoffs, competitors, new sourcing channels).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
