&lt;li&gt;Upper-Intermediate or higher level of English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in technical recruitment, talent sourcing, or recruitment coordination in a fast-paced environment (software, fintech, gamedev or similar).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience sourcing/recruiting in the US market.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive sourcing skills (LinkedIn Recruiter, Boolean search).&lt;/li&gt;
