&lt;li&gt;Experience with ATS (Greenhouse, Lever, or similar) is highly beneficial.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and negotiation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently, proactively in a fast-paced, high-performance environment with high-quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills, attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ownership mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
